Summary: Two star like lights moving together paralel.
divs: sighting detailsi went to take the trash out about 8:15 on 9\8\09. as i turned around from the garbage cans i noticed a very bright light in the sky. i first thought it was a star. i then saw another bright light directly above it. they were vertical coming from the west. the lights were moving together and they looked to be a city block in length from each other. i said to myself "what the hell is that??!!!" i went and got my boyfriend. we both watched it. it just seemed to move and float right over our backyard and then turned and went to the north. i couldnt see it any longer because of the trees and house. i have lived near an airport all my life and never have witness anything like this in my life. commercial jets have a flashing light, this had none. this was definately, unidentifiable.
